# ═══ Default-DENY gitignore for the public research repo ═══
# Everything is ignored unless explicitly allowed. Only external PDFs under
# reports/ (plus the index files) can ever be committed.

# 1) deny everything
*

# 2) allow the repo's own files
!.gitignore
!README.md
!DISCLAIMER.md
!PUBLISH.md

# 3) allow reports/ — PDFs and .gitkeep only
!reports/
!reports/**/
!reports/**/*.pdf
!reports/**/.gitkeep

# 4) re-deny dangerous shapes everywhere (belt and braces)
**/*_internal.*
**/*.py
**/*.md.bak
**/.env*
**/*.key
**/*apikey*
**/*secret*
**/*credentials*
